com.microsoft.bingads.v11.reporting
Class ReportingDownloadOperation

java.lang.Object
  com.microsoft.bingads.v11.reporting.ReportingDownloadOperation

public class ReportingDownloadOperation
extends Object

Reserved for internal use. Represent a reporting download operation requested by a user. You can use it to poll for the download operation status, and then download the results file when available.
